Class QuizFillInTheBlanksController

    • thebabycareproject.QuizFillInTheBlanksController

    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class QuizFillInTheBlanksController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Controller of the subsection ' quizFillInTheBlanks ' of the section ' Quiz ' of the ' Edu-care ' category. Provides three images with three text fields. One have to write answer in these fields according to the questions.
